ps://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"d0f9024f3e43cd27f0c4bb6c67104479ed8ec724","tid":1666980,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏嘅同我入嚟<br />\n快啲把握最好時機</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}